    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/evaluation-of-the-deepened-co-location-trials"/>
    <title>Evaluation of the deepened co-location trials</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Presents findings from case study visits to 8 of the 22 jobcentres that took part in joint location trials with Next Steps.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;BIS research paper no. 98. Presents findings from case study visits to 8 of the 22 Jobcentres that took part in the joint location trials with Next Step (now known as the National Careers Service).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It highlights key issues arising from the research with a view to contributing to the success of the wider roll out of joint location in Jobcentres in England.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
