    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Outlines the government’s priorities for capital funding plans for the remainder of this Parliament and aspirations for future capital investment in further education (FE) colleges. Sets out key priorities, and it encourages colleges to develop coherent property strategies capable of a phased implementation to maximise the impact of capital grant availability. Also includes some FE college capital project case studies. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
